-- Hedge funds have exacerbated equity sell-off -Fidelity's Rossi
-- By Sudip Kar-Gupta
-- Thu Oct 16, 2014 07:24AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Oct 16 (Reuters) - The worldwide equity sell-off of the last two weeks has been exacerbated by the "poor positioning" of many investors, including hedge funds, said Fidelity Worldwide Investments' equities global chief investment officer Dominic Rossi.

